description._content: Description: Group of Islanders: This group includes practically the entire inhabitants. Location: Tristan Da Cunha Date: 1920-1929 Description: The Sea Front: Edinburgh, the Settlement, on the right. Location: Tristan Da Cunha Date: 1920-1929 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/776 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
